sub_title: Communications Advisor and Head of the communications department at Hubrecht Institute
summary:
During my PhD and my studies I observed that I find a lot of joy in learning about science and telling others about scientific advances. In addition, I find contact with others very inspiring. Therefore I am very happy to work as communication officer of the Hubrecht Institute. Here I can combine my curiosity for science with spreading scientific discoveries and interactions with many different people. 

In my spare time I like to cook, read, sing, create things en play board games.
